{"legislative_session": "20252026", "identifier": "AB2186", "title": "Personal Income Tax Law: exclusions: reparations programs.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["PersonalIncomeTaxLaw", "exclusions", "reparationsprograms"], "abstracts": [{"note": "summary", "abstract": "The Personal Income Tax Law, in modified conformity with federal income tax laws, defines \"gross income\" as income from whatever source derived, except as specifically excluded, and provides various exclusions from gross income. \n\nThis bill, for taxable years beginning on or after January 1, 2027, and before January 1, 2032, would exclude from gross income any reparations benefit or payment, as defined, received by a taxpayer during the taxable year.\n\nExisting law requires any bill authorizing a new tax expenditure to contain, among other things, specific goals, purposes, and objectives that the tax expenditure will achieve, detailed performance indicators, and data collection requirements.\n\nThis bill also would include additional information required for any bill authorizing a new tax expenditure. \n\nThis bill would take effect immediately as a tax levy."}], "other_titles": [{"note": "", "title": "Pharmacy."}], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-ca-20252026-ab2186"}], "actions": [{"description": "Read first time. To print.", "date": "2026-02-19", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["reading-1"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "From printer. May be heard in committee March 22.", "date": "2026-02-20", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Referred to Com. on REV. & TAX.", "date": "2026-03-16", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on REV. & TAX.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee chair, with author's amendments: Amend, and re-refer to Com. on REV. & TAX. Read second time and amended.", "date": "2026-03-16", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["amendment-introduction", "amendment-passage", "reading-1", "reading-2"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Re-referred to Com. on REV. & TAX.", "date": "2026-03-17", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on REV. & TAX.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "In committee: Set, first hearing. Referred to REV. & TAX. suspense file.", "date": "2026-04-13", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "REV. & TAX. suspense file.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}, {"name": "REV. & TAX", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "From committee: Do pass and re-refer to Com. on APPR. (Ayes 5. Noes 2.) (April 27). Re-referred to Com. on APPR.", "date": "2026-04-28", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["committee-passage", "committee-passage-favorable", "referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Com. on APPR.", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}], "sponsorships": [{"name": "McKinnor", "classification": "author", "entity_type": "person", "primary": true, "person_id": "~{\"name\": \"McKinnor\"}", "organization_id": null}], "related_bills": [], "versions": [{"note": "AB2186", "links": [{"url": "http://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/billNavClient.xhtml?bill_id=202520260AB2186", "media_type": "text/html"}], "date": "", "classification": ""}, {"note": "02/19/26 - Introduced", "links": [{"url": "https://leginfo.legislature.ca.gov/faces/billPdf.xhtml?bill_id=202520260AB2186&version=20250AB2186